### USER LIST
GET {{host}}/users/users/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json


### Search users
GET {{host}}/users/users/?search=jk
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json


### USER LOGOUT
POST {{host}}/users/logout/
Authorization: Bearer {{varvar_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh": "{{refresh_token}}"
}

### USER PROFILE 
GET {{ host }}/users/profile/
Authorization: Bearer {{ access_token }}
Content-Type: application/json


### ANOTHER PROFILE 
GET {{ host }}/users/another-profile/2/
Authorization: Bearer {{ varvar_token }} 
Content-Type: application/json


### CREATE MUSIC
POST {{host}}/posts/musics/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "music_name": "This is a new music",
  "music_file": "media/posts/images/main.txt",
  "author": 3
}


### CREATE POST
POST {{host}}/posts/posts/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "This is a new post",
  "image": "media/posts/images/star.jpeg",
  "caption": "There is a lot of things to do",
  "author_id": 2
}


### CREATE STORY
POST {{host}}/posts/stories/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "image": "media/posts/images/star.jpeg",
  "author_id": 2
}


### GET STORY
GET {{host}}/posts/stories/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json



### Like POST
POST {{host}}/posts/posts/10/like_toggle/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}



### Save POST
POST {{host}}/posts/posts/10/save_toggle/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}



